 31 -def escape_to_python(string): 

 32      """escape a given .rc string into a valid Python string""" 
 33      pystring = re.sub('"\s*\\\\\n\s*"', "", string)   # xxx"\n"xxx line continuation 
 34      pystring = re.sub("\\\\\\\n", "", pystring)       # backslash newline line continuation 
 35      pystring = re.sub("\\\\n", "\n", pystring)        # Convert escaped newline to a real newline 
 36      pystring = re.sub("\\\\t", "\t", pystring)        # Convert escape tab to a real tab 
 37      pystring = re.sub("\\\\\\\\", "\\\\", pystring)   # Convert escape backslash to a real escaped backslash 
 38      return pystring
